公司介紹與職缺詳情

Uber
Uber 透過手機 App 與司機連結，使城市中的行動變的更方便，並給司機更多的業務和人們更多乘車的選擇。Uber 2009年成立於美國舊金山，至今全球已超過466個城市，Uber 為世界帶來新的移動方式，並縮短人們和城市的距離！
不管在美國、歐洲或亞洲的各大城市，無論時間地點，只需開啟Uber 手機app，簡單註冊並填寫信用卡資料後，輕觸叫車按鈕，車子就會在 5 -10 分鐘內抵達您指定的上車地點。
Uber 我們秉持高度熱情，致力讓城市更加完善。基於上述目標，我們與數千名在地朋友共同合作，維持臺北運輸順暢運作。我們還對於刺激當地經濟活絡運作不遺餘力，協助市街更加安全不受酒醉駕駛行為所威脅，積極促進交通運輸更為順暢通達。
我們期待優秀的你能將創意提升至另一境界，造福人們的日常生活便利。有些事物為真實世界帶來了改變—且進展迅速。我們仍有漫漫長路需要不斷努力。您可協助我們早日實現目標。
Uber 粉絲頁
工作地點
臺北市光復南路102號4樓
應徵方式
請直接於企業官網應徵
<1. Operation and Logistic Associate – Taipei | 1 名>
工作內容 
1. Be the voice and face of Uber. Manage in-person communications (both 1-1 and 1-many) between Uber and its driver community.
2.Contribute to rapid growth. Work onsite to manage the process of on boarding new drivers and support existing partners.
3.Be a process master. Constantly innovate and iterate to ensure maximum productivity in our processes.
4.Manage efficiency. Plan, track, order, and disburse equipment to driver partners.
5.Help us scale faster. Work closely with the driver operations and logistics teams to streamline process.
必備經歷與能力
1.B.A. or B.S. (Recent graduates encouraged to apply!)
2.Strong communication skills and ability to interact with internal and external partners
3.Superior organisational skills and great follow through on tasks
4.Be a problem solver at heart with a genuine interest in learning by doing
5.An interest in and passion for Uber
<2. Operations & Logistics Manager – Taipei | 1 名>
工作內容 
Uber is a marketplace, and our Operations & Logistics managers own the entire “supply” side of that marketplace in their city – they optimize the quantity and quality of cars available to our users, and continually improve the rider experience via scheduling, asset utilization, and driver incentive programs.
In practice this requires a unique mix of analytical and interpersonal skills; an ability to use our data to quickly understand trends in supply and user demand, combined with an ability to motivate and incent our partners to behave in ways that take advantage of those insights. Highly refined people skills, as well as toughness, persistence and grit, are required to ensure capacity, while providing the quality of service we demand for our users. This is an intense, business-side startup role which has a clear and direct, impact on the growth of our business.
必備經歷與能力
1. Language – The ability to speak, read and write Mandarin Chinese fluently
2.Analytical ability – We take an intensely data-driven approach to running our business. In order to efficiently manage the supply of cars we have on the road, you need to be able to constantly monitor and understand trends in supply and demand, and use our data to make the right, data-driven operational decisions.
3.Business instincts – Inherently curious by nature, you enjoy thinking about what makes different businesses tick. You’d be excited to master Uber’s business model, and would doggedly pursue making that model flourish in your city.
4.Drive and hustle – Operations & Logistics managers are responsible for continually sourcing, signing up, onboarding and motivating the fleet of drivers who are our partners in a city. This requires extreme resourcefulness, and the ability to sell Uber as a partner and platform. Operations Managers also constantly monitor the fleet of cars on the road at any given point in time, optimizing the quantity of cars, guiding their physical location across the city, based on user demand, and ensuring the highest levels of service. This requires the constant focus and the highest levels of dedication.
5.People skills – You’ll need truly world-class people skills to be able to influence partners to drive at times, in places, and in ways that ensure a world-class experience for our users. Depending on the conversation, you’ll need to be able to charm or cajole our partners accordingly.
<3. Taiwan Expansion Manager | 1 名>
工作內容 
Expansion Managers are responsible for using their analytical, creative and people skills to bring Uber to new markets. You will be traveling around Taiwan growing Uber from the ground up, so we need the best. If that’s you, get excited!
1.Researching your city and learning the transportation pain points, regulations and market opportunity for Uber.
2.Engaging with local municipalities and stakeholders to understand local needs and build a model and foundation for success.
3.Creating and executing local marketing strategies to encourage user adoption and penetration for Uber of the market.
4.Setting up partnerships and managing relationships with drivers to get the supply side ready for Uber’s launch.
5.Exploring business development opportunities (sponsorships, partnerships, and co-marketing promotions) to increase awareness and visibility of Uber in local communities.
6.Finding, hiring and guiding a team to help run day-to-day operations of the city.
Throwing a baller event to get Uber off the ground.
必備經歷與能力
1. 3+ years of marketing or operations management experience (or related).
2.Experience creating, executing, and tracking a marketing plan.
3.Prior experience managing cross-functional teams.
4.Successfully executed business development opportunities and negotiating partnerships.
5.Have weathered early startup environment.
6.BA degree in business, finance or marketing (MBA a-plus).
7.Native fluency in Mandarin Chinese (read, write, speak) and living and working experience in Taiwan. Fluency in Taiwanese dialect a plus.
回求職機會總覽

EZTABLE
EZTABLE 是台灣第一家專門提供消費者 24hrs 餐廳網路訂位、提供餐廳飯店 訂位管理系統 的網路平臺，
目前全台灣、香港、泰國及印尼等地已超過 9000 家餐廳加入EZTABLE , 超過 10,000,000人次透過 EZTABLE 訂位到餐廳用餐!
主要合作的餐廳包括喜來登、君悅、六福皇宮、W Hotel、漢來海港 等飯店集團，及 王品集團、瓦城、Lawry’s、Robuchon 、R A W 等餐飲集團與高級餐廳。
EZTABLE 一直希望能透過網路的服務帶來更便利的生活。
同時我們希望能學習矽谷創業文化，用更開放的工作方式與態度，共同為一個目標來努力。
除了有良好工作環境、也提供學習及成長的空間，歡迎優秀的朋友一起加入 EZTABLE 的工作行列!
工作地點
臺北市大安區敦化南路二段216號14樓
應徵方式
career@eztable.com 或直接於  人力銀行 應徵
<1. EZTABLE 實體店 經理 Store Manager | 1 名>
工作內容 
1. 推廣線上餐廳預訂及餐券服務
2. 協助消費者順利完成線上預訂餐廳、購買餐券，排解困難，創造珍貴聚餐回憶
3. 熟悉 EZTABLE 各項服務功能與用途，瞭解消費者意見並提出改善方式
4. 挑戰各類危機處理、問題協調，轉化為美好用餐體驗
5. 門市商圈經營
必備經歷與能力
1. 服務業店長相關工作經驗尤佳
2. 個性樂觀開朗、臨危不亂，理解力與記憶力佳，能處理多重專案
3. 面對客戶具備細心與耐心
4. 喜歡網路服務，對新科技新功能有興趣、容易上手尤佳
5. 接受假日排班（輪休）
6. 善於溝通及表達
<2. 業務經理 Sales Manager | 2 名>
工作內容 
1. 開發五星級飯店與中高端餐廳客戶、拓展市場，拜訪並完成銷售，開啓合作關係
2. 分析潛在客戶現況、需求與發展潛力，主動提案最佳合作方案，確保業績目標達成
3. 反應客戶需求統整與回報、建立客戶與 EZTABLE 之間優質溝通橋樑
4. 建立餐飲業豐沛人脈資源，即時瞭解最新情報消息
必備經歷與能力
1. 口條好、表達能力佳、說服力強、不怕挫折
2. 具有業務銷售經驗
<3. Full-stack Engineer | 1 名>
工作內容 
Are you interested in building products used by thousands of people around the world? Do you like shipping code at a rapid pace? EZTABLE is seeking an experienced engineer who is passionate about building an excellent service!
Job Description:
– Work with architect to improve the system architecture.
– Build scalable service and maintain online service.
– Collaborate with product managers and designers to create feature specifications.
必備經歷與能力
* Required Skills:
– Proficient in PHP or NodeJS
– Excellent in Javascript, HTML, CSS
– Familiar with Linux.
– Basic Understanding of SQL/NOSQL.
– Familiar with Version Control tools.
* Personality:
– Problem solver
– Team player
– Passionate
– Foodie
* Nice to have:
– Experiences in JS Frameworks, ex. React.js, D3.js and etc
– Familiar with AWS, Docker
