<1. Head of Operations, Taiwan | 1 名>
工作內容 
You will have the opportunity to develop and oversee the supply part of our platform in Taiwan. You will lead the operational side of solution development, from planning to coordinating and implementation. You will find yourself working a lot of the below:
1. Actively leading supply side strategy
2. Define and settle efficiency leads
3. Set, standardize and optimize metrics
4. Formalize dedicated SOP for standard product and contingency management
5. Analyze and provide operational market opportunities and risks
6. Anticipate operational issues and define solutions and action plans
7. Communicate with all team members
必備經歷與能力
1.Driver Focused: You need to be obsessed with what makes drivers “tick”. Your ability to understand and communicate with our partners is the essential component to scaling quality delivery
2.Data Driven: Data is your best friend. Break down lots of data into meaningful pieces to inform your strategy and guide your daily execution. Test, learn, iterate, and repeat.
3.Self-Starter: a strong entrepreneurial spirit and work ethic will be critical to setting the example for the team you build. Setting goals and metrics and defining roles and responsibilities are key parts to the role.
4.Solution Oriented: the market moves quickly and not everything will go as planned. Consequently, you will need to make decision and adapt based on new information you will be receiving on a daily basis. You embrace challenges as opportunities rather than problems and you use a structured approach to evaluate your progress.
5. Logistic and/or consulting background
6. Significant field experience
7. B2C e-commerce experience is highly valuable
8. Experienced in SQL, Excel or other data management tools
9. Proficiency in dissecting data and transforming into actionable strategies
10. Autonomous, flexible and dedicated. Team player
11. Good command of English
12. Immediate availability preferred
