<3. Product Manager, (HK-based) | 2 名>
工作內容 
At Lalamove, you will work with star engineers and designers in a fast-paced, rapidly growing, enthusiastic company. This role demands a lot of outside of the box thinking, technical depth, innovation, and focus on the end-user. You will drive the product direction and strategy to ensure that it is aligned with the business focus. You will own the product roadmap and its KPIs. You will conduct A/B tests while understanding user behavior and needs. In addition, you will be required to perform market research and competitor analyses to ensure that our product dominates its competition!
What We Seek:
1. Passion: passion for building cool products (bonus points if you’ve built your own mobile app or website!)
2. Strong leadership and motivator: in this role you will be managing a team of developers, so you need to be able to motivate and lead the team to continue to innovate and build
3. Innovator: innovation is a key characteristic that we look for because as a technology company it is important to continue to think outside of the box and generate new ideas
4. Ability to juggle many tasks: the ability to multitask and stay organized is a necessity at our company, all while making sure that new features and updates are rolled out in a timely manner
必備經歷與能力
1. At least 3-5 years of experience in software and mobile development
2. Extensive knowledge and understanding of mobile and web technologies
3. Business or engineering degree preferred
4. Prior experience as a developer is an advantage
5. Demonstrate ability and comfort to work closely with engineers on a daily basis
6. Excellent interpersonal and communications skills
7. High-quality planning and organizational capabilities
8. Good team player, self-motivated, and strong leadership skills
