3. Use your knowledge of testing and testability to influence better software design, promote best engineering practices, bug prevention strategies, testability, and other quality attributes across products.
必備經歷與能力
1. Experience with test methodologies, writing test plans, creating test cases and debugging.
2. Experience with tests automation.
回求職機會總覽

